  <summary date="2021-07-27T00:05:09Z" status="Passed House">Divided Families Reunification Act

This bill directs the Department of State to periodically report to Congress on its consultations with South Korea&#160;on potential opportunities to reunite Korean Americans with family in North Korea. The State Department's Special Envoy on North Korean Human Rights Issues shall periodically report to Congress on its&#160;consultations with representatives of Korean Americans with family in North Korea on reunification efforts.</summary>
